Circulating proteins as predictors of cardiovascular mortality in end-stage 
renal disease.

Feldreich T(1)(2)(3), Nowak C(2), Fall T(3), Carlsson AC(2)(3), Carrero JJ(4), 
Ripsweden J(5), Qureshi AR(6), Heimbürger O(6), Barany P(6), Stenvinkel P(6), 
