[Considerations of elderly patient's dental rehabilitation treated with 
bisphophonate].

[Article in Hungarian; Abstract available in Hungarian from the publisher]

Bata Z(1), Vasziné Szabó E(1), Tóth Z(1).

Author information:
(1)Konzerváló Fogászati Klinika, Semmelweis Egyetem, Fogorvostudományi Kar 
